[package]
name = "rocket_auth"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["tvallotton@uc.cl"]
description = "A high level authentication management library for Rocket applications. It supports both SQLite and Postgres."
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["rocket", "users", "authentication", "auth", "session"]
categories = ["web-programming"]
license = "MIT or Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/tvallotton/rocket_auth"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true
[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1.50"
chashmap = "2.2.2"
chrono = "0.4.19"
fehler = "1.0.0"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
rand = "0.8.3"
regex = "1"
rust-argon2 = "0.8.3"
serde_json = "1.0.59"
thiserror = "1.0.25"

[dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3.16"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.rocket]
version = "0.5.0-rc.2"
features = ["secrets"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.125"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.5.5"
features = []
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.4.0"
features = ["rt", "rt-multi-thread"]
optional = false

[dependencies.validator]
version = "0.14.0"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false
[dev-dependencies.rocket]
version = "0.5.0-rc.2"
features = ["secrets", "json"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies.rocket_auth]
path = "../rocket_auth"
features = ["sqlx-sqlite", "sqlx-mysql"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies.rocket_dyn_templates]
version = "0.1.0-rc.2"
features = ["tera"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.5.5"
features = ["runtime-tokio-rustls"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies.tokio-postgres]
version = "0.7.0"
features = []
optional = false

[features]
sqlx-mysql = ["sqlx/mysql"]
sqlx-sqlite = ["sqlx/sqlite"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "rocket_auth"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2018"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
